{"tid":342718,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國駐聯合國代表：朝鮮半島問題須美國與北韓解決 而不是中國","createTime":"2017-07-31T23:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T11:24:58.000Z","uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"31a5f8104748768c15c89a207570a42acc4438fd","tid":342718,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:20:28.000Z","msg":"陸代表：朝鮮半島問題須美與北韓解決<br />\n<br />\n2017-08-01 05:44<br />\n<br />\n〔中央社〕中國大陸常駐聯合國代表劉結一今天表示，如何設法緩和緊張並恢復談判以推動朝鮮半島非核化，取決於美國和北韓，而不是中國大陸。<br />\n<br />\n劉結一在大陸7月輪值聯合國安全理事會主席任務完成的記者會中說；「<span style=\"color: red;\">他們對保持情勢進展並開始朝正確方向邁進，負有主要責任，而不是中國。」</span><br />\n<br />\n他說：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">無論中國多麼能幹，中國的努力都不會產生實際結果，因為這取決於主要的雙方。</span></span>」<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"3d761913582561ed69c6261fd68e121fe191a6dd","tid":342718,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哇 中國射波"},{"pid":"166c169b0f08d57fb699a3b869642e63d7ef3368","tid":342718,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:24:36.000Z","msg":"唔撚係大國勃起咩？<br />\n<br />\n又要靠美國出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bbd0be8085e259d6552ae7e8820947c50ab41d","tid":342718,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:25:04.000Z","msg":"互射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扯下貓尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f593c7e05449ede250cc94aca93e5d26b2fab760","tid":342718,"uid":609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:25:26.000Z","msg":"廢柴國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac887a26d43edcd2e3d0bf4d3ae3fd393a5b8e45","tid":342718,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係話<br />\n支那已經廢到連北韓都管唔到<br />\n咁你仲有咩用？"},{"pid":"7679034c09fe85f696ecb3dd9f06fd41d9cb9b88","tid":342718,"uid":60655,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:32:31.000Z","msg":"侵侵：咁我擺薩德你咪咁多野講"},{"pid":"ab5b8808f0cf69f8340b819dc5606b31287f3f57","tid":342718,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T23:51:07.000Z","msg":"北韓問題難解 川普怒：我對中國太失望了！<br />\n<br />\n2017-07-30 10:21<br />\n<br />\n川普再批中國對北韓問題光說不練。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國總統川普日前曾公開批評中國對北韓制裁不夠力，稍早又在推特上認為中國可以輕鬆解決北韓問題，並表示「對中國太失望了！」<br />\n<br />\n北韓接連發射飛彈，北韓當局自稱洲際彈道飛彈（ICBM）能夠打擊美國本土，包括洛杉磯、丹佛與芝加哥都在其射程範圍內，波士頓與紐約則「可能」剛好落在射程內。川普在美國時間29日連發2則貼文，把矛頭指向長期對美國貿易順差的中國。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">川普的兩則貼文寫道，「我對中國太失望了！過去我們（美國）愚蠢的領袖容許中國每年在貿易上賺走上千億美元，然而...」另一篇貼文續寫，「他們（中國）卻對北韓『毫無作為』、『光說不練』我們不再允許這種情況，中國大可輕鬆解決北韓問題！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n日前也傳出，中國未能符合美國期待制衡北韓，據傳美國總統川普已失去耐心了，有美國官員透露，數週內可能會針對與北韓有往來的中國企業與小型銀行進行新的制裁。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpd3S31u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpd3S31u.jpg&h=ad8b170a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2147537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2147537&d=Tn%2F0yZDUumzN1QvX0F5%2FI6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=3bbce6d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2147537&h=ed5779fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2147537</a>"},{"pid":"92c51adb6b48988a1f71f2040934901bde5818f5","tid":342718,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,